OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FPlenty of
OL,6,Flate sunshine to end the day. Dry
OL,7,Fovernight, with some low cloud
OL,8,Freturning to eastern areas, western
OL,9,Fareas holding on to the clearer skies.
OL,10,
OL,11,CFriday:FAny morning cloud clearing to
OL,12,Fleave another dry and sunny day. The
OL,13,Fsunshine turning hazy at times in the
OL,14,Fafternoon. Remaining hot, though a
OL,15,Flittle cooler towards the northwest.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
